    docker pull nginx
    docker images
-> Detail information about docker image
    docker inspect <docker image name>
> meta data of the docker image in json format


-> give the docker logs with conatiner name
    docker logs <conatiner name/id>
-> creating a container with automatic port mapping
    docker run -d -P nginx
-> detail information about the container, shows the error why container is exited, or any other error in the running container.
    docker logs <container name>
-> to set a variable in the container we use {-e}
    docker run -d -P -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD-mypass mysql:5.7
    
